    "data": [
        {
            "title": "利比亞軍方總參謀長在土耳其墜機事故中身亡",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:利比亞;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/利比亞\">利比亞</a>國際承認的政府表示，一架搭載利比亞軍方總參謀長Mohammed Ali Ahmed al-Haddad的私人飛機在土耳其中部墜毀。此前當局與該飛機失聯，事故造成Haddad及另外4人遇難。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">土耳其內政部長Ali Yerlikaya在X平台發文稱，這架獵鷹50飛機於周二晚間從安卡拉飛往利比亞的黎波裡途中失聯，隨後在Haymana鎮附近發現飛機殘骸。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據Yerlikaya介紹，飛機於當地時間20點10分從安卡拉埃森博阿機場(Esenboga Airport)起飛，在靠近Haymana鎮附近報告請求緊急降落，但在大約20點52分之後無法再與其取得聯繫。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e3fb5005-f90a-37af-a78f-425964fce5e8-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據FlightRadar24的數據，這架達索獵鷹50機齡為37年，由Harmony Jets運營。該飛機於12月22日從的黎波裡飛抵安卡拉。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">的黎波裡政府表示，機上乘客還包括利比亞陸軍首領Fattouri Gharbil中將。此外，利比亞軍事工業化服務處負責人Mahmoud al-Fadhawi准將、顧問Mohammed al-Asawy以及攝影師Mohammed al-Mahjoub也在機上。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">土耳其總參謀長Selcuk Bayraktaroglu周二早些時候曾接待Haddad，並舉行了由兩國高級指揮官出席的雙邊及代表團級別會談。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Libya’s Military Chief of Staff Dies in Jet Crash in Turkey (2)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Sherif Tarek.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%88%A9%E6%AF%94%E4%BA%9E%E8%BB%8D%E6%96%B9%E7%B8%BD%E5%8F%83%E8%AC%80%E9%95%B7%E5%9C%A8%E5%9C%9F%E8%80%B3%E5%85%B6%E5%A2%9C%E6%A9%9F%E4%BA%8B%E6%95%85%E4%B8%AD%E8%BA%AB%E4%BA%A1-210035014.html",
