        {
            "title": "諾比侃首掛飆3.6倍 每手賺14550",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span>3隻新股同於周二（23日）登場，首日表現上演冰火兩重天。內地人工智能科技公司諾比侃（02635）收報371元，較招股價80元，顯著抽高3.64倍或291元，一手50股，賬面賺14550元；股份成交額達2.24億元。</span></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">數字綜合健康服務及健康保險解決方案平台輕鬆健康（02661）開市報50元，較招股價22.68元，漲1.2倍，最高見59.8元，升逾1.6倍，全日收報58.7元，升近1.58倍或36.02元。一手200股，賬面賺7204元；股份成交額3.2億元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>翰思艾泰潛水46%</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">至於尚未有盈利的生物科技公司翰思艾泰（03378）開市報28.9元，較招股價32元跌9.7%；該股以全日最低位的17.2元收市，瀉46.3%。一手100股，賬面蝕1480元；全日成交額2.32億元。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-bc7efc3c-61ce-355d-ab53-b3ab37deecf4-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日前掛牌的尚未盈利生科股華芢生物（02396）昨日再跌18.89%，收報21.9元，上市僅兩天累挫42.67%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">人工智能（AI）驅動藥物發現及開發公司英矽智能（03696）周二中午截飛。消息指出，其公開發售吸引了22.2萬人入飛，錄超額認購1430倍，涉及3290億元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>壁仞暫超購97倍</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">同樣周二截飛的中國高端護膚品牌林清軒（02657），據悉公開發售錄超額認購1238倍，涉1358億元，共吸引了17萬人認購。此外，市場消息稱，中國數字孿生科技公司五一視界（06651）公開發售部分錄得超額認購258倍，涉約95億元；吸引約4.4萬人入飛。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「國產GPU四小龍」之一的壁仞科技（06082）步入招股第二天，截至周二晚約7時，券商暫為其借出239.97億元孖展，以公開發售集資額2.43億元計，相當於超額認購逾97倍。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%AB%BE%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%83%E9%A6%96%E6%8E%9B%E9%A3%863-6%E5%80%8D-%E6%AF%8F%E6%89%8B%E8%B3%BA14550-182200399.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-24 02:30:53",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美國國債小幅走低 最新GDP數據打擊降息預期",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國國債小幅走低，此前發布的GDP數據顯示美國經濟創出兩年來最快增速，打擊了市場對2026年降息的預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">各期限國債殖利率均上升，其中兩年期國債殖利率漲幅最大，上漲3個基點至3.52%，交易員下調對貨幣政策前景鴿派程度的押注。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：美國第三季度經濟成長4.3% 創出兩年來最快增速</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周二公佈的數據顯示，第三季度經通膨調整後的國內生產毛額折合年率成長4.3%。經濟學家此前預期為3.3%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-3ed3eca2-cf83-3511-81ab-e67f3e372c29-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「數據顯示GDP高於預期後，市場遭受劇烈衝擊，」Mischler Financial Group董事總經理Tom di Galoma表示，「現貨交易依然清淡，但期貨賣盤卻相當活躍。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/CqOLeIij4PFPSbS3yeuAqQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/fcaa875fd609df05eaa47da0e12fb833\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">投資者下調了對明年降息的押注，目前認為聯儲會在1月28日的會議上降息的可能性只有17%左右。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周二晚些時候，美國財政部將發行700億美元的五年期國債，屆時市場將再次面臨需求考驗。周一發行的兩年期國債獲穩健需求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Treasuries Slip as US GDP Posts Fastest Growth in Two Years</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%8B%E5%82%B5%E5%B0%8F%E5%B9%85%E8%B5%B0%E4%BD%8E-%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0gdp%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E6%89%93%E6%93%8A%E9%99%8D%E6%81%AF%E9%A0%90%E6%9C%9F-144302998.html",
